
# Commands to apply Bayesian neural network to an image classification problem.

net-spec ilog1.net 36 80 4 / ih=0.05:4::1.2 bh=0.5:2 ho=1.5:5::4 bo=0.1:2
model-spec ilog1.net class

data-spec ilog1.net 36 1 4 / idata@1:1000 . idata@1001:3000 .

net-gen ilog1.net fix 0.1
mc-spec ilog1.net repeat 15 heatbath hybrid 100:10 0.15
net-mc ilog1.net 1

mc-spec ilog1.net sample-sigmas heatbath hybrid 1500:30 0.3
net-mc ilog1.net 5000

net-pred mnpa ilog1.net 1001:
